\v 27 <a name="02400702700004" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">Dir</a>-lhes-<a name="02400702700004" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">ás</a>, pois, todas estas <a name="02400702700014" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavras</a>, mas não te <a name="02400702700024">darão</a> <a name="02400702700024">ouvidos</a>; <a name="02400702700030" ll="SDBH:קרא:000000">chamá</a>-los-<a name="02400702700030" ll="SDBH:קרא:000000">ás</a>, mas não <a name="02400702700038" ll="SDBH:ענה:000000">te</a> <a name="02400702700038" ll="SDBH:ענה:000000">responderão</a>. 
