\v 13 Eis que eu sou contra ti, ó <a name="02402101300006">Moradora</a> do <a name="02402101300010" ll="SDBH:עֵמֶק:000000">vale</a>, ó <a name="02402101300012" ll="SDBH:צוּר:000001">Rocha</a> da <a name="02402101300016" ll="SDBH:מִישֹׁור:000000">campina</a>, <a name="02402101300018;02402101300020" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">diz</a> <a name="02402101300018;02402101300020" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">o</a> <a name="02402101300018;02402101300020" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">Senhor</a>; contra vós outros <a name="02402101300024" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">que</a> <a name="02402101300024" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizeis</a>: Quem <a name="02402101300028" ll="SDBH:נחת:000000">descerá</a> contra nós? Ou: Quem <a name="02402101300036">entrará</a> nas <a name="02402101300040" ll="SDBH:מְעֹנָה:000000">nossas</a> <a name="02402101300040" ll="SDBH:מְעֹנָה:000000">moradas</a>? 
