\v 6 Porque assim <a name="02402200600006" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> o <a name="02402200600008" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> acerca da <a name="02402200600012" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">casa</a> do <a name="02402200600014" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> de <a name="02402200600016" ll="SDBH:יְהוּדָה:000000">Judá</a>: Tu és para mim <a name="02402200600018" ll="SDBH:גִּלְעָד:000001" il="tb031315454;tb060403135">Gileade</a> e a <a name="02402200600024" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:000011">cabeça</a> do <a name="02402200600028" ll="SDBH:לְבָנֹון:000000" il="Lebanon_mountains">Líbano</a>; mas certamente <a name="02402200600034" ll="SDBH:שׁית:000003">farei</a> <a name="02402200600034" ll="SDBH:שׁית:000003">de</a> <a name="02402200600034" ll="SDBH:שׁית:000003">ti</a> um <a name="02402200600036" ll="SDBH:מִדְבָּר:000000" il="RS26447_ISR91T-418;Sinai-191;Sinai-220;Sinai-3;Sinai178;Sinai190;tb113006604">deserto</a> e <a name="02402200600038" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000" tl="HOTTP3400">cidades</a> <a name="02402200600040;02402200600044" ll="SDBH:לֹא:000000" tl="HOTTP3400">desabitadas</a>. 
