\v 9 Então, se lhes <a name="02402200900004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">responderá</a>: Porque <a name="02402200900010" ll="SDBH:עזב:000006">deixaram</a> a <a name="02402200900014" ll="SDBH:בְּרִית:000000">aliança</a> <a name="02402200900016" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">do</a> <a name="02402200900016" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, <a name="02402200900018" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">seu</a> <a name="02402200900018" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">Deus</a>, e <a name="02402200900022" ll="SDBH:חוה:001000" il="Prostrate_figures">adoraram</a> a <a name="02402200900028" ll="SDBH:אַחֵר:000000">outros</a> <a name="02402200900026" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000000">deuses</a>, e <a name="02402200900032" ll="SDBH:עבד:000002">os</a> <a name="02402200900032" ll="SDBH:עבד:000002">serviram</a>.
    
\v 10 Não <a name="02402201000004" ll="SDBH:בכה:000000">choreis</a> o <a name="02402201000008" ll="SDBH:מות:000000">morto</a>, nem o <a name="02402201000014" ll="SDBH:נוד:000003">lastimeis</a>; <a name="02402201000018" ll="SDBH:בכה:000000">chorai</a> <a name="02402201000020" ll="SDBH:בכה:000000">amargamente</a> aquele <a name="02402201000026" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001">que</a> <a name="02402201000026" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001">sai</a>; porque nunca mais <a name="02402201000032" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000023">tornará</a>, nem <a name="02402201000038" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">verá</a> a <a name="02402201000042" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> <a name="02402201000044" ll="SDBH:מֹולֶדֶת:000000">onde</a> <a name="02402201000044" ll="SDBH:מֹולֶדֶת:000000">nasceu</a>. 
