\v 26 Até quando <a name="02402302600008" tl="HOTTP3408">sucederá</a> isso no <a name="02402302600012" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001" tl="HOTTP3408">coração</a> dos <a name="02402302600016" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profetas</a> que <a name="02402302600018" ll="SDBH:נבא:000000">proclamam</a> <a name="02402302600022" ll="SDBH:שֶׁקֶר:000000">mentiras</a>, que <a name="02402302600026" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">proclamam</a> só o <a name="02402302600028" ll="SDBH:תַּרְמִית:000000">engano</a> <a name="02402302600030" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">do</a> <a name="02402302600030" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">próprio</a> <a name="02402302600030" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">coração</a>? 
