\v 28 O <a name="02402302800004" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profeta</a> que tem <a name="02402302800010" ll="SDBH:חֲלֹום:000000" il="tb112004059w">sonho</a> <a name="02402302800012" ll="SDBH:ספר:000006">conte</a>-o como apenas <a name="02402302800014" ll="SDBH:חֲלֹום:000000" il="tb112004059w">sonho</a>; mas aquele em quem está a <a name="02402302800020" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">minha</a> <a name="02402302800020" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavra</a> <a name="02402302800024" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">fale</a> a <a name="02402302800026" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">minha</a> <a name="02402302800026" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavra</a> com <a name="02402302800028" ll="SDBH:אֱמֶת:000000">verdade</a>. Que tem a <a name="02402302800036" ll="SDBH:תֶּבֶן:000000">palha</a> com o <a name="02402302800042" ll="SDBH:בַּר:002000">trigo</a>? — <a name="02402302800044;02402302800046" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">diz</a> <a name="02402302800044;02402302800046" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">o</a> <a name="02402302800044;02402302800046" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">Senhor</a>. 
\v 29 Não é a <a name="02402302900008" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">minha</a> <a name="02402302900008" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavra</a> <a name="02402302900014" ll="SDBH:אֵשׁ:000000" il="Fire02">fogo</a>, <a name="02402302900016;02402302900018" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">diz</a> <a name="02402302900016;02402302900018" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">o</a> <a name="02402302900016;02402302900018" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">Senhor</a>, e <a name="02402302900024" ll="SDBH:פַּטִּישׁ:000000" il="Realia:1.12.1a;Realia:1.12.1b">martelo</a> que <a name="02402302900026" ll="SDBH:פצץ:000000">esmiúça</a> a <a name="02402302900028" ll="SDBH:סֶלַע:000000">penha</a>? 
\v 30 Portanto, eis que eu sou contra esses <a name="02402303000010" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profetas</a>, <a name="02402303000012;02402303000014" ll="SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">diz</a> <a name="02402303000012;02402303000014" ll="SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">o</a> <a name="02402303000012;02402303000014" ll="SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">Senhor</a>, que <a name="02402303000016" ll="SDBH:גנב:000000">furtam</a> as <a name="02402303000018" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">minhas</a> <a name="02402303000018" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">palavras</a>, <a name="02402303000020">cada</a> <a name="02402303000020">um</a> ao <a name="02402303000026" ll="SDBH:רֵעַ:001000">seu</a> <a name="02402303000026" ll="SDBH:רֵעַ:001000">companheiro</a>. 
\v 31 Eis que eu sou contra esses <a name="02402303100008" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profetas</a>, <a name="02402303100010;02402303100012" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">diz</a> <a name="02402303100010;02402303100012" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">o</a> <a name="02402303100010;02402303100012" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">Senhor</a>, que <a name="02402303100016" ll="SDBH:לקח:000000">pregam</a> a <a name="02402303100018" ll="SDBH:לָשֹׁון:000000">sua</a> própria <a name="02402303100018" ll="SDBH:לָשֹׁון:000000">palavra</a> e <a name="02402303100022" ll="SDBH:נאם:000000">afirmam</a>: Ele <a name="02402303100024" ll="SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">disse</a>. 
\v 32 Eis que eu sou contra os <a name="02402303200006" ll="SDBH:נבא:000000">que</a> <a name="02402303200006" ll="SDBH:נבא:000000">profetizam</a> <a name="02402303200008" ll="SDBH:חֲלֹום:000000" il="tb112004059w">sonhos</a> <a name="02402303200010" ll="SDBH:שֶׁקֶר:000000">mentirosos</a>, <a name="02402303200012;02402303200014" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">diz</a> <a name="02402303200012;02402303200014" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">o</a> <a name="02402303200012;02402303200014" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">Senhor</a>, e <a name="02402303200018" ll="SDBH:ספר:000006">os</a> <a name="02402303200018" ll="SDBH:ספר:000006">contam</a>, e com as <a name="02402303200030" ll="SDBH:שֶׁקֶר:000000">suas</a> <a name="02402303200030" ll="SDBH:שֶׁקֶר:000000">mentiras</a> e <a name="02402303200036" ll="SDBH:פַּחֲזוּת:000000">leviandades</a> <a name="02402303200022" ll="SDBH:תעה:000003">fazem</a> <a name="02402303200022" ll="SDBH:תעה:000003">errar</a> o <a name="02402303200026" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">meu</a> <a name="02402303200026" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a>; pois eu não <a name="02402303200044" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">os</a> <a name="02402303200044" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">enviei</a>, nem <a name="02402303200050" ll="SDBH:צוה:000000">lhes</a> <a name="02402303200050" ll="SDBH:צוה:000000">dei</a> <a name="02402303200050" ll="SDBH:צוה:000000">ordem</a>; e também <a name="02402303200054;02402303200056;02402303200058" ll="SDBH:יעל:000001;SDBH:לֹא:000000">proveito</a> <a name="02402303200054;02402303200056;02402303200058" ll="SDBH:יעל:000001;SDBH:לֹא:000000">nenhum</a> <a name="02402303200054;02402303200056;02402303200058" ll="SDBH:יעל:000001;SDBH:לֹא:000000">trouxeram</a> a este <a name="02402303200064">povo</a>, <a name="02402303200070;02402303200072" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">diz</a> <a name="02402303200070;02402303200072" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">o</a> <a name="02402303200070;02402303200072" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">Senhor</a>.
    
\v 33 Quando, pois, este <a name="02402303300010" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> <a name="02402303300006" ll="SDBH:שׁאל:000000">te</a> <a name="02402303300006" ll="SDBH:שׁאל:000000">perguntar</a>, ou qualquer <a name="02402303300020" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profeta</a>, ou <a name="02402303300024" ll="SDBH:כֹּהֵן:000000" il="LB00263">sacerdote</a>, <a name="02402303300028" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: Qual é a sentença <a name="02402303300032" ll="SDBH:מַשָּׂא:000004">pesada</a> do <a name="02402303300034" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>? Então, lhe <a name="02402303300038" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dirás</a>: Vós sois o <a name="02402303300046" ll="SDBH:מַשָּׂא:000004" tl="HOTTP3410">peso</a>, e eu vos <a name="02402303300050" ll="SDBH:נטשׁ:000003">arrojarei</a>, <a name="02402303300054;02402303300056" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">diz</a> <a name="02402303300054;02402303300056" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">o</a> <a name="02402303300054;02402303300056" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">Senhor</a>. 
\v 34 Quanto ao <a name="02402303400006" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profeta</a>, e ao <a name="02402303400012" ll="SDBH:כֹּהֵן:000000" il="LB00263">sacerdote</a>, e ao <a name="02402303400018" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a> que <a name="02402303400022" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disser</a>: Sentença <a name="02402303400024" ll="SDBH:מַשָּׂא:000004">pesada</a> do <a name="02402303400026" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, a esse <a name="02402303400036">homem</a> eu <a name="02402303400030" ll="SDBH:פקד:000006">castigarei</a> e a <a name="02402303400046" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000003">sua</a> <a name="02402303400046" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000003">casa</a>. 
\v 35 Antes, <a name="02402303500004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">direis</a>, <a name="02402303500006" ll="SDBH:אִישׁ:000002">cada</a> <a name="02402303500006" ll="SDBH:אִישׁ:000002">um</a> ao <a name="02402303500010" ll="SDBH:רֵעַ:001000">seu</a> <a name="02402303500010" ll="SDBH:רֵעַ:001000">companheiro</a> e <a name="02402303500014" ll="SDBH:אִישׁ:000002">cada</a> <a name="02402303500014" ll="SDBH:אִישׁ:000002">um</a> ao <a name="02402303500018" ll="SDBH:אָח:000005">seu</a> <a name="02402303500018" ll="SDBH:אָח:000005">irmão</a>: Que <a name="02402303500022" ll="SDBH:ענה:000000">respondeu</a> o <a name="02402303500024" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>? Que <a name="02402303500030" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">falou</a> o <a name="02402303500032" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>? 
\v 36 Mas nunca mais <a name="02402303600010" ll="SDBH:זכר:000000">fareis</a> <a name="02402303600010" ll="SDBH:זכר:000000">menção</a> da sentença <a name="02402303600004" ll="SDBH:מַשָּׂא:000004">pesada</a> do <a name="02402303600006" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>; porque a <a name="02402303600024">cada</a> <a name="02402303600024">um</a> lhe servirá de sentença <a name="02402303600018" ll="SDBH:מַשָּׂא:000004">pesada</a> a <a name="02402303600026" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">sua</a> <a name="02402303600026" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">própria</a> <a name="02402303600026" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavra</a>; pois <a name="02402303600030" ll="SDBH:הפך:000006">torceis</a> as <a name="02402303600034" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavras</a> do <a name="02402303600036" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000002">Deus</a> <a name="02402303600038" ll="SDBH:חַי:000000">vivo</a>, do <a name="02402303600040" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> <a name="02402303600042" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000006">dos</a> <a name="02402303600042" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000006">Exércitos</a>, o <a name="02402303600044" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">nosso</a> <a name="02402303600044" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">Deus</a>. 
\v 37 Assim <a name="02402303700004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dirás</a> ao <a name="02402303700010" ll="SDBH:נָבִיא:000000">profeta</a>: Que te <a name="02402303700014" ll="SDBH:ענה:000000">respondeu</a> o <a name="02402303700016" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>? Que <a name="02402303700022" ll="SDBH:דבר:001000">falou</a> o <a name="02402303700024" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>? 
\v 38 <a name="02402303800004">Mas</a>, porque <a name="02402303800010" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizeis</a>: Sentença <a name="02402303800006" ll="SDBH:מַשָּׂא:000004">pesada</a> do <a name="02402303800008" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, assim o <a name="02402303800016" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> o <a name="02402303800018">Senhor</a>: Porque <a name="02402303800022" ll="SDBH:אמר:000001">dizeis</a> esta <a name="02402303800028" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000002">palavra</a>: Sentença <a name="02402303800034" ll="SDBH:מַשָּׂא:000004">pesada</a> do <a name="02402303800036">Senhor</a> (<a name="02402303800040" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">havendo</a>-vos <a name="02402303800040" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000000">eu</a> <a name="02402303800048;02402303800050" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000;SDBH:לֹא:000000">proibido</a> <a name="02402303800048;02402303800050" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000;SDBH:לֹא:000000">de</a> <a name="02402303800048;02402303800050" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000;SDBH:לֹא:000000">dizerdes</a> esta palavra: Sentença <a name="02402303800052" ll="SDBH:מַשָּׂא:000004">pesada</a> do <a name="02402303800054">Senhor</a>), 
\v 39 por isso, <a name="02402303900008" tl="HOTTP3411">levantar</a>-vos-<a name="02402303900008" tl="HOTTP3411">ei</a> e vos <a name="02402303900016" ll="SDBH:נטשׁ:000003">arrojarei</a> da <a name="02402303900044">minha</a> <a name="02402303900044">presença</a>, a vós outros e à <a name="02402303900026" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">cidade</a> que vos <a name="02402303900030">dei</a> e a <a name="02402303900038" ll="SDBH:אָב:000001">vossos</a> <a name="02402303900038" ll="SDBH:אָב:000001">pais</a>. 
\v 40 <a name="02402304000004">Porei</a> sobre vós <a name="02402304000010" ll="SDBH:עֹולָם:000000">perpétuo</a> <a name="02402304000008" ll="SDBH:חֶרְפָּה:000000">opróbrio</a> e <a name="02402304000016" ll="SDBH:עֹולָם:000000">eterna</a> <a name="02402304000014" ll="SDBH:כְּלִמּוּת:000000">vergonha</a>, que jamais <a name="02402304000022" ll="SDBH:שׁכח:000000">será</a> <a name="02402304000022" ll="SDBH:שׁכח:000000">esquecida</a>.
\c 24
\v 1 <a name="02402400100002" ll="SDBH:ראה:000003">Fez</a>-<a name="02402400100002" ll="SDBH:ראה:000003">me</a> <a name="02402400100002" ll="SDBH:ראה:000003">ver</a> o <a name="02402400100004" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, e vi <a name="02402400100010" ll="SDBH:שְׁנַיִם:000000">dois</a> <a name="02402400100012" ll="SDBH:דּוּד:000000" il="Bolen00042;HK00332">cestos</a> de <a name="02402400100014" ll="SDBH:תְּאֵנָה:000000" il="Flora:2.6b;Flora:2.6d;figs1691, rp;tb092506030">figos</a> <a name="02402400100016" ll="SDBH:יעד:000000">postos</a> <a name="02402400100020">diante</a> do <a name="02402400100022" ll="SDBH:הֵיכָל:000000">templo</a> do <a name="02402400100024" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, <a name="02402400100026" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:001002">depois</a> <a name="02402400100026" ll="SDBH:אַחַר:001002">que</a> <a name="02402400100030" ll="SDBH:נְבוּכַדְרֶאצַּר:000000" il="Processional_Way,_Babylon;jc1229149058;mat13229">Nabucodonosor</a>, <a name="02402400100032" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="02402400100034" ll="SDBH:בָּבֶל:000000" il="HK00224;Ishtar_gate;Processional_Way,_Babylon;Satellite Bible Atlas00070;Satellite Bible Atlas00071;jc1229149058;mat07384;mat13229">da</a> <a name="02402400100034" ll="SDBH:בָּבֶל:000000" il="HK00224;Ishtar_gate;Processional_Way,_Babylon;Satellite Bible Atlas00070;Satellite Bible Atlas00071;jc1229149058;mat07384;mat13229">Babilônia</a>, <a name="02402400100028" ll="SDBH:גלה:000013" il="Babylon_exile_Fugel;Exile_Lachish;Exile_after_Lachish;Jehu-Obelisk-cropped;Lachish_Relief-exile;tb112004312">levou</a> <a name="02402400100028" ll="SDBH:גלה:000013" il="Babylon_exile_Fugel;Exile_Lachish;Exile_after_Lachish;Jehu-Obelisk-cropped;Lachish_Relief-exile;tb112004312">em</a> <a name="02402400100028" ll="SDBH:גלה:000013" il="Babylon_exile_Fugel;Exile_Lachish;Exile_after_Lachish;Jehu-Obelisk-cropped;Lachish_Relief-exile;tb112004312">cativeiro</a> a <a name="02402400100038" ll="SDBH:יְהֹויָכִין:000000">Jeconias</a>, <a name="02402400100040" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000000">filho</a> <a name="02402400100042" ll="SDBH:יְהֹויָקִים:000000">de</a> <a name="02402400100042" ll="SDBH:יְהֹויָקִים:000000">Jeoaquim</a>, <a name="02402400100044" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="02402400100046" ll="SDBH:יְהוּדָה:000000">de</a> <a name="02402400100046" ll="SDBH:יְהוּדָה:000000">Judá</a>, e os <a name="02402400100052" ll="SDBH:שַׂר:000000">príncipes</a> de <a name="02402400100054" ll="SDBH:יְהוּדָה:000000">Judá</a>, e os <a name="02402400100062" ll="SDBH:חָרָשׁ:000000">artífices</a>, e os <a name="02402400100070" ll="SDBH:מַסְגֵּר:000000" il="Realia:1.11.2">ferreiros</a> de <a name="02402400100074" ll="SDBH:יְרוּשָׁלַ͏ִם:000000" il="NBGbs20090227-1_14;NBGbs20090227-1_34;NBGbs20090425-1_54;NBGbs20110228-1_79;Satellite Bible Atlas00024;jlm_hezekiah_city_d03;jlm_topography_d04">Jerusalém</a> e os <a name="02402400100078">trouxe</a> à <a name="02402400100080" ll="SDBH:בָּבֶל:000000" il="HK00224;Ishtar_gate;Processional_Way,_Babylon;Satellite Bible Atlas00070;Satellite Bible Atlas00071;jc1229149058;mat07384;mat13229">Babilônia</a>. 
\v 2 Tinha <a name="02402400200006" ll="SDBH:אֶחָד:000000">um</a> <a name="02402400200004" ll="SDBH:דּוּד:000000" il="Bolen00042;HK00332">cesto</a> <a name="02402400200008" ll="SDBH:תְּאֵנָה:000000" il="Flora:2.6b;Flora:2.6d;figs1691, rp;tb092506030">figos</a> <a name="02402400200012" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001">muito</a> <a name="02402400200010" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000000">bons</a>, como os <a name="02402400200016" ll="SDBH:תְּאֵנָה:000000" il="Flora:2.6b;Flora:2.6d;figs1691, rp;tb092506030">figos</a> <a name="02402400200020" ll="SDBH:בִּכּוּרָה:000000" il="Flora:2.6b;Flora:2.6d">temporãos</a>; mas o <a name="02402400200026;02402400200028" ll="SDBH:אֶחָד:000000;SDBH:דּוּד:000000" il="Bolen00042;HK00332">outro</a>, <a name="02402400200030;02402400200032" ll="SDBH:רַע:000000;SDBH:תְּאֵנָה:000000" il="Flora:2.6b;Flora:2.6d;figs1691, rp;tb092506030">ruins</a>, que, <a name="02402400200044" ll="SDBH:רֹעַ:000000">de</a> <a name="02402400200044" ll="SDBH:רֹעַ:000000">ruins</a> <a name="02402400200034" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001">que</a> <a name="02402400200034" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001">eram</a>, não <a name="02402400200040" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">se</a> <a name="02402400200040" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">podiam</a> <a name="02402400200040" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">comer</a>. 
\v 3 Então, me <a name="02402400300004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">perguntou</a> o <a name="02402400300006" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>: Que <a name="02402400300014" ll="SDBH:ראה:000000">vês</a> tu, <a name="02402400300016" ll="SDBH:יִרְמְיָה:000003">Jeremias</a>? <a name="02402400300020" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">Respondi</a>: <a name="02402400300022" ll="SDBH:תְּאֵנָה:000000" il="Flora:2.6b;Flora:2.6d;figs1691, rp;tb092506030">Figos</a>; os <a name="02402400300026" ll="SDBH:תְּאֵנָה:000000" il="Flora:2.6b;Flora:2.6d;figs1691, rp;tb092506030">figos</a> <a name="02402400300034" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001">muito</a> <a name="02402400300030;02402400300032" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000000">bons</a> e os <a name="02402400300044" ll="SDBH:מְאֹד:000001">muito</a> <a name="02402400300040;02402400300042" ll="SDBH:רַע:000000">ruins</a>, que, de <a name="02402400300054" ll="SDBH:רֹעַ:000000">ruins</a> que são, <a name="02402400300050" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">não</a> <a name="02402400300050" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">se</a> <a name="02402400300050" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">podem</a> <a name="02402400300050" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">comer</a>.
    
\v 4 A mim me veio a <a name="02402400400006" ll="SDBH:דָּבָר:000000">palavra</a> <a name="02402400400008" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">do</a> <a name="02402400400008" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, <a name="02402400400014" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: 
\v 5 Assim <a name="02402400500004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> o <a name="02402400500006" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, o <a name="02402400500008" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">Deus</a> de <a name="02402400500010" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a>: Do modo por que vejo estes <a name="02402400500020" ll="SDBH:טֹוב:000000">bons</a> <a name="02402400500016" ll="SDBH:תְּאֵנָה:000000" il="Flora:2.6b;Flora:2.6d;figs1691, rp;tb092506030">figos</a>, assim <a name="02402400500028;02402400500056" ll="SDBH:טֹובָה:000000;SDBH:נכר:000001">favorecerei</a> os <a name="02402400500032" ll="SDBH:גָּלוּת:000001">exilados</a> de <a name="02402400500034" ll="SDBH:יְהוּדָה:000000">Judá</a>, que <a name="02402400500038" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000007">eu</a> <a name="02402400500038" ll="SDBH:שׁלח:000007">enviei</a> deste <a name="02402400500044" ll="SDBH:מָקֹום:000000">lugar</a> para a <a name="02402400500050" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> dos <a name="02402400500052" ll="SDBH:כַּשְׂדִּים:001000" il="HK00224;Ishtar_gate;Processional_Way,_Babylon;Satellite Bible Atlas00070;adr1306212742;jc1229149058;mat07384;mat13229">caldeus</a>. 
\v 6 <a name="02402400600004" ll="SDBH:שׂים:000036">Porei</a> sobre eles <a name="02402400600012" ll="SDBH:טֹובָה:000001">favoravelmente</a> <a name="02402400600006" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">os</a> <a name="02402400600006" ll="SDBH:עַיִן:000000">olhos</a> e <a name="02402400600016" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000051">os</a> <a name="02402400600016" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000051">farei</a> <a name="02402400600016" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000051">voltar</a> para esta <a name="02402400600022" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a>; <a name="02402400600030" ll="SDBH:בנה:000000">edificá</a>-<a name="02402400600030" ll="SDBH:בנה:000000">los</a>-<a name="02402400600030" ll="SDBH:בנה:000000">ei</a> e não os <a name="02402400600036" ll="SDBH:הרס:000001">destruirei</a>, <a name="02402400600040" ll="SDBH:נטע:000000" il="A_Tamarind_tree_seedling;LB00094;tb0309169388">plantá</a>-<a name="02402400600040" ll="SDBH:נטע:000000" il="A_Tamarind_tree_seedling;LB00094;tb0309169388">los</a>-<a name="02402400600040" ll="SDBH:נטע:000000" il="A_Tamarind_tree_seedling;LB00094;tb0309169388">ei</a> e não os <a name="02402400600046" ll="SDBH:נתשׁ:000003">arrancarei</a>. 
\v 7 <a name="02402400700004">Dar</a>-lhes-<a name="02402400700004">ei</a> <a name="02402400700008" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">coração</a> para que me <a name="02402400700012">conheçam</a> que eu sou o <a name="02402400700020" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>; eles serão o meu <a name="02402400700030" ll="SDBH:עַם:000000">povo</a>, e eu serei o seu <a name="02402400700042" ll="SDBH:אֱלֹהִים:000001">Deus</a>; porque <a name="02402400700046" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000005">se</a> <a name="02402400700046" ll="SDBH:שׁוב:000005">voltarão</a> para mim de todo o <a name="02402400700054" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">seu</a> <a name="02402400700054" ll="SDBH:לֵב:000001">coração</a>.
    
