\v 23 Eles <a name="02402602300004" ll="SDBH:יצא:000001">tiraram</a> a <a name="02402602300008" ll="SDBH:אוּרִיָּה:000004">Urias</a> do <a name="02402602300012" ll="SDBH:מִצְרַיִם:000001" il="Egyptian_temple;Gizah_Pyramids;Goshen;NBGbs20120205-81;NBGbs20120205-82;NBGbs20120207-20;NBGbs20140204-40;tb010705951">Egito</a> e o <a name="02402602300016">trouxeram</a> ao <a name="02402602300022" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="02402602300024" ll="SDBH:יְהֹויָקִים:000000">Jeoaquim</a>; este mandou <a name="02402602300028">feri</a>-<a name="02402602300028">lo</a> à <a name="02402602300034" ll="SDBH:חֶרֶב:000001" il="NBGmk20130711a;NBGmk20130711b;NBGmk20130711c;StraightSword-02-003;adr1305240787;tb061616732">espada</a> e <a name="02402602300038" ll="SDBH:שׁלך:000000">lançar</a>-lhe o <a name="02402602300042" ll="SDBH:נְבֵלָה:000000">cadáver</a> nas <a name="02402602300046" ll="SDBH:קֶבֶר:000000" il="tb031115105">sepulturas</a> da <a name="02402602300048;02402602300052" ll="SDBH:בֵּן:000003;SDBH:עַם:000000">plebe</a>. 
