\v 34 Não <a name="02403103400006" ll="SDBH:למד:000001">ensinará</a> jamais <a name="02403103400010">cada</a> <a name="02403103400010">um</a> ao <a name="02403103400014" ll="SDBH:רֵעַ:001000">seu</a> <a name="02403103400014" ll="SDBH:רֵעַ:001000">próximo</a>, nem <a name="02403103400018">cada</a> <a name="02403103400018">um</a> ao <a name="02403103400022" ll="SDBH:אָח:000005">seu</a> <a name="02403103400022" ll="SDBH:אָח:000005">irmão</a>, <a name="02403103400026" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizendo</a>: <a name="02403103400028">Conhece</a> ao <a name="02403103400032" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, porque todos me <a name="02403103400038">conhecerão</a>, desde o <a name="02403103400046" ll="SDBH:קָטָן:000002">menor</a> até ao <a name="02403103400052" ll="SDBH:גָּדֹול:000002">maior</a> <a name="02403103400052" ll="SDBH:גָּדֹול:000002">deles</a>, <a name="02403103400054;02403103400056" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">diz</a> <a name="02403103400054;02403103400056" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">o</a> <a name="02403103400054;02403103400056" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">Senhor</a>. Pois <a name="02403103400060" ll="SDBH:סלח:000000">perdoarei</a> as <a name="02403103400064" ll="SDBH:עָוֹן:000000">suas</a> <a name="02403103400064" ll="SDBH:עָוֹן:000000">iniquidades</a> e dos <a name="02403103400070" ll="SDBH:חַטָּאת:000000">seus</a> <a name="02403103400070" ll="SDBH:חַטָּאת:000000">pecados</a> jamais me <a name="02403103400074" ll="SDBH:זכר:000000">lembrarei</a>.
    
\v 35 Assim <a name="02403103500004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> o <a name="02403103500006" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>, que <a name="02403103500008">dá</a> o <a name="02403103500010" ll="SDBH:שֶׁמֶשׁ:000000" il="Sun;Sunrise;Sunset">sol</a> para a <a name="02403103500014" ll="SDBH:אֹור:000000">luz</a> do <a name="02403103500016" ll="SDBH:יֹומָם:000000">dia</a> e as <a name="02403103500018" ll="SDBH:חֻקָּה:000001" tl="HOTTP3445">leis</a> <a name="02403103500018" ll="SDBH:חֻקָּה:000001" tl="HOTTP3445">fixas</a> à <a name="02403103500020" ll="SDBH:יָרֵחַ:000000">lua</a> e às <a name="02403103500024" ll="SDBH:כֹּוכָב:000000" il="Stars">estrelas</a> para a <a name="02403103500028" ll="SDBH:אֹור:000000">luz</a> da <a name="02403103500030" ll="SDBH:לַיְלָה:000000">noite</a>, que <a name="02403103500032" ll="SDBH:רגע:001000">agita</a> o <a name="02403103500036" ll="SDBH:יָם:000000" il="Rough_seas">mar</a> e <a name="02403103500040" ll="SDBH:המה:000000">faz</a> <a name="02403103500040" ll="SDBH:המה:000000">bramir</a> as <a name="02403103500042" ll="SDBH:גַּל:000000" il="Breaking_waves,_Sète_cf03;Rough_seas">suas</a> <a name="02403103500042" ll="SDBH:גַּל:000000" il="Breaking_waves,_Sète_cf03;Rough_seas">ondas</a>; <a name="02403103500044" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> <a name="02403103500046" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000006">dos</a> <a name="02403103500046" ll="SDBH:צָבָא:000006">Exércitos</a> é o <a name="02403103500048" ll="SDBH:שֵׁם:000000">seu</a> <a name="02403103500048" ll="SDBH:שֵׁם:000000">nome</a>. 
