\v 37 Assim <a name="02403103700004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> o <a name="02403103700006" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>: Se <a name="02403103700010" ll="SDBH:מדד:000000">puderem</a> <a name="02403103700010" ll="SDBH:מדד:000000">ser</a> <a name="02403103700010" ll="SDBH:מדד:000000">medidos</a> os <a name="02403103700012" ll="SDBH:שָׁמַיִם:000001">céus</a> lá <a name="02403103700018" ll="SDBH:מַעַל:001000">em</a> <a name="02403103700018" ll="SDBH:מַעַל:001000">cima</a> e <a name="02403103700022" ll="SDBH:חקר:000000">sondados</a> os <a name="02403103700024" ll="SDBH:מֹוסָד:000000">fundamentos</a> <a name="02403103700026" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">da</a> <a name="02403103700026" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> cá <a name="02403103700030" ll="SDBH:מַטָּה:000000">embaixo</a>, também eu <a name="02403103700036" ll="SDBH:מאס:000000">rejeitarei</a> toda a <a name="02403103700042" ll="SDBH:זֶרַע:000004" il="Children_of_Kabul,_Afghanistan">descendência</a> de <a name="02403103700044" ll="SDBH:יִשְׂרָאֵל:000000">Israel</a>, por tudo quanto <a name="02403103700052">fizeram</a>, <a name="02403103700054;02403103700056" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">diz</a> <a name="02403103700054;02403103700056" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">o</a> <a name="02403103700054;02403103700056" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000;SDBH:נְאֻם:000000">Senhor</a>.
    
