\v 28 Portanto, assim <a name="02403202800006" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> o <a name="02403202800008">Senhor</a>: Eis que <a name="02403202800012">entrego</a> esta <a name="02403202800018" ll="SDBH:עִיר:000000">cidade</a> nas <a name="02403202800026">mãos</a> dos <a name="02403202800030" ll="SDBH:כַּשְׂדִּים:001000" il="HK00224;Ishtar_gate;Processional_Way,_Babylon;Satellite Bible Atlas00070;adr1306212742;jc1229149058;mat07384;mat13229">caldeus</a>, nas <a name="02403202800036">mãos</a> de <a name="02403202800038" ll="SDBH:נְבוּכַדְרֶאצַּר:000000" il="Processional_Way,_Babylon;jc1229149058;mat13229">Nabucodonosor</a>, <a name="02403202800040" ll="SDBH:מֶלֶךְ:000000">rei</a> <a name="02403202800042" ll="SDBH:בָּבֶל:000000" il="Ishtar_gate">da</a> <a name="02403202800042" ll="SDBH:בָּבֶל:000000" il="Ishtar_gate">Babilônia</a>, e <a name="02403202800046" ll="SDBH:לכד:000000">ele</a> <a name="02403202800046" ll="SDBH:לכד:000000">a</a> <a name="02403202800046" ll="SDBH:לכד:000000">tomará</a>. 
