\v 26 <a name="02404802600002" ll="SDBH:שׁכר:000002">Embriagai</a>-<a name="02404802600002" ll="SDBH:שׁכר:000002">o</a>, porque contra o <a name="02404802600008" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> <a name="02404802600010" ll="SDBH:גדל:000007">se</a> <a name="02404802600010" ll="SDBH:גדל:000007">engrandeceu</a>; <a name="02404802600016" ll="SDBH:מֹואָב:000001" il="Bolen00033;Satellite Bible Atlas00006">Moabe</a> <a name="02404802600014" ll="SDBH:ספק:001000">se</a> <a name="02404802600014" ll="SDBH:ספק:001000">revolverá</a> no <a name="02404802600020" ll="SDBH:קִיא:000000">seu</a> <a name="02404802600020" ll="SDBH:קִיא:000000">vômito</a> e será ele também <a name="02404802600028" ll="SDBH:שְׂחֹוק:000001">objeto</a> <a name="02404802600028" ll="SDBH:שְׂחֹוק:000001">de</a> <a name="02404802600028" ll="SDBH:שְׂחֹוק:000001">escárnio</a>. 
